title: My mate got b5 after winning 8 games and loosing 2
body: Hey, my mate is shocked after being pumped for the new season and getting right into ranked games. He carryed every single game getting a positive KDA in every one and ended up getting 8 wins and only 2 looses. Yet he has been placed in b5 how!?!??!

replies.body: How do u think i feel, i won all 10 and got put in b5. I made a post earlier about it.
